{"prompt": "Design a portfolio for a product manager. The site should be organized, featuring a clean bright yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Product Manager Portfolio - [Your Name]</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFDA61; /* Bright Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #FFF8E1; /* A lighter, softer yellow */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --dark-text-color: #222222;\n            --light-text-color: #555555;\n            --border-color: #F0C84A;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #F0C84A 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #about, #projects, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about h2, #projects h2, #contact h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        #about .bio {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        #about .bio img {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 5px solid var(--border-color);\n        }\n\n        #about .bio-text {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #about .bio-text h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .project-item {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .project-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .project-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .project-item p {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .project-item a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project-item a:hover {\n            background: var(--border-color);\n        }\n\n        #projects .projects-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #contact ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact li {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        #contact a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact a:hover {\n            color: var(--border-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            border-top: #F0C84A 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            #about .bio {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            #about .bio img {\n                margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Your Name]</h1>\n            <p>Product Manager | Driving Innovation & Delivering Value</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <div class=\"bio\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200\" alt=\"Your Photo\">\n                <div class=\"bio-text\">\n                    <h3>Passionate about building products people love.</h3>\n                    <p>I am a results-oriented Product Manager with [Number] years of experience in [Industry/Domain]. I excel at bridging the gap between business goals, user needs, and technical feasibility. My approach is data-driven, user-centric, and collaborative, ensuring successful product launches and continuous improvement.</p>\n                    <p>Specialties include: Product Strategy, Roadmapping, User Research, Agile Methodologies, Cross-functional Team Leadership, Go-to-Market Strategy.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"projects\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Projects</h2>\n            <div class=\"projects-grid\">\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h3>Project Title 1</h3>\n                    <p>Brief description of the project, highlighting your role and achievements. Focus on the problem solved and the impact delivered. Example: Led the development of a new mobile feature, resulting in a 15% increase in user engagement.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#project-link-1\" target=\"_blank\">View Case Study</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h3>Project Title 2</h3>\n                    <p>Another project example. Emphasize your contributions and the measurable outcomes. Example: Defined the product roadmap for a SaaS platform, contributing to a 20% revenue growth.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#project-link-2\" target=\"_blank\">View Case Study</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h3>Project Title 3</h3>\n                    <p>Third project example. Showcase your ability to manage complex products or challenges. Example: Spearheaded user research initiatives that informed the redesign of a core product, improving user satisfaction by 25%.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#project-link-3\" target=\"_blank\">View Case Study</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Let's connect and discuss how I can bring value to your team.</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Email: <a href=\"mailto:your.email@example.com\">your.email@example.com</a></li>\n                <li>LinkedIn: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yourprofile/\" target=\"_blank\">linkedin.com/in/yourprofile</a></li>\n                <li>Portfolio URL (optional): <a href=\"[Your Portfolio URL]\" target=\"_blank\">[Your Portfolio URL]</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Your Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n<script>\n    // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for anchor links\n    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n        anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n\n            document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                behavior: 'smooth'\n            });\n        });\n    });\n</script>"}